<hr>
  <section class="main-section" id="Strawberry_Field">
    <header>Strawberry Field</header>
    <p>A delicious but very sweet cocktail, tastes like those strawberry sweets.</p>
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <code><li>Strawberry Puree 50ml</li><li>Peach Puree 50ml</li><li>Vanilla Syrup 50ml</li><li>Pink Gin 35ml</li><li>Passion Fruit 35ml</li><li>Soda Water 100ml</li></code>
    <h3>Directions</h3><p>Pour it all into a shaker and shake. Careful as sodawater is fizzy. Pour into glass with crushed ice.</p>
</section>
<hr>
  <section class="main-section" id="Rockstar_Martini">
    <header>Rockstar Martini</header>
    <p>A local version of a classic cocktail</p>
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <code><li>Mount Gay Rum 50ml</li><li>Passoa 15ml</li><li>Lime Juice 15ml</li><li>Pineapple Juice 30ml</li><li>Vanilla clear stuff monin 15ml</li></code>
    <h3>Directions</h3> <p>Pour it all into a shaker and shake, pour into glass.</p>
  </section>
<hr>
  <section class="main-section" id="Blue_Lagoon">
    <header>Blue Lagoon</header>
    <p>A local version of a classic cocktail</p>
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <code><li>Vodka 50ml</li><li>Blue Stuff 50ml</li><li>Lemonade 200ml</li></code>
    <h3>Directions</h3> <p>Pour it all into a shaker and shake. Pour into glass with crushed ice.</p>
  </section>
<hr>
  <section class="main-section" id="Pornstar_Martini">
    <header>Pornstar Martini</header>
    <p>A classic cocktail, served with a single shot of Prosecco</p>
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <code><li>Vanilla Vodka 50ml</li><li>Vanilla Syrup 15ml</li><li>Passion Fruit Juice 100ml</li><li>A tea spoon of lime juice</li><li>15ml passion fruit puree</li></code>
    <h3>Directions</h3> <p>Pour it all into a shaker and shake, pour into glass.</p>
  </section>
<hr>
  <section class="main-section" id="Bootylicious">
    <header>Bootylicious</header>
    <p>A local bar's cocktail</p>
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <code><li>Vodka 1.5 shots</li><li>.75 Shot Strawberry Liquere</li><li>1.5 Shots Passion Juice</li><li>1.5 Shots Apple Juice</li></code>
    <h3>Directions</h3> <p>Pour it all into a shaker with ice and shake hard, pour into glass.</p>
  </section>
